<Body><Title>四川雅江县发生重大道路交通事故 造成17死2伤</Title>
<ReportTime type="absTime">2011-11-24 9:35:43</ReportTime>
<Content><Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e1" type="thoughtevent"><Participant sid="s1">中新网</Participant><Location lid="l1">雅江</Location><Time tid="t1" type="relTime">11月23日</Time><Denoter did="d1" type="statement">电</Denoter></Event>(刘忠俊)<Event eid="e2" type="thoughtevent"><Participant sid="s2">记者</Participant><Time tid="t2" type="relTime">23日晚间</Time>从<Participant oid="o2">四川甘孜州政府办</Participant><Denoter did="d2" type="statement">获悉</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e3">该州境内的<Location lid="l3">雅江县</Location>发生一起重大<Denoter did="d3" type="emergency">交通事故</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e4">已造成<Participant sid="s4">17人</Participant><Denoter did="d4" type="stateChange">死亡</Denoter></Event><Event eid="e5"><Participant sid="s5">2人</Participant><Denoter did="d5" type="stateChange">受伤</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph>
　　<Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e6" type="thoughtevent">据<Participant sid="s6">雅江县政府</Participant><Denoter did="d6" type="statement">报告</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e7"><Time tid="t7" type="relTime">23日13时35分左右</Time>，<Location lid="l7">雅江县恶古乡境内</Location><Object sid="s7">一辆农用车</Object><Denoter did="d7" type="action">车载</Denoter><Participant oid="o7">19人</Participant></Event>，<Event eid="e8">发生重大道路<Denoter did="d8" type="emergency">交通事故</Denoter> </Event>，<Event eid="e9">致<Participant sid="s9">17人</Participant><Denoter did="d9" type="stateChange">死亡</Denoter></Event>(其中1名小孩)，<Event eid="e10"><Participant sid="s10">2人</Participant><Denoter did="d10" type="stateChange">受伤</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence><Sentence>伤者中有1人伤势较重。</Sentence></Paragraph>
　　<Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e11"><Denoter did="d11" type="action">接到</Denoter><Object oid="o11">事故报告</Object></Event>后，<Event eid="e12"><Participant sid="s12,s11,s13">甘孜州委、州政府</Participant>立即<Denoter did="d12" type="action">启动</Denoter><Object oid="o12">重大交通事故应急预案</Object></Event>，<Event eid="e13">迅速<Denoter did="d13" type="operation">成立</Denoter>事故调查处理<Participant oid="o13">工作组</Participant></Event>，<Event eid="e14">相关领导率安监、公安、卫生等<Participant sid="s14,s15,s16">工作组</Participant><Denoter did="d14" type="movement">赶赴</Denoter><Location lid="l14">事故现场</Location></Event><Event eid="e15">展开<Denoter did="d15" type="action">善后</Denoter></Event>及<Event eid="e16"><Object oid="o16">事故</Object><Denoter did="d16" type="operation">调查</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence><Sentence><Event eid="e17"><Participant sid="s17">甘孜州相关领导</Participant>要求要<Denoter did="d17" type="action">采取</Denoter>一切<Object oid="o17">措施</Object></Event><Event eid="e18"><Denoter did="d18" type="operation">抢救</Denoter><Participant oid="o18">伤员</Participant></Event>，<Event eid="e19">最大限度<Denoter did="d19" type="stateChange">减少</Denoter><Object oid="o19">伤亡</Object></Event>，<Event eid="e20">迅速<Denoter did="d20" type="action">开展</Denoter>事故调查处理<Object oid="o20">工作</Object></Event>，<Event eid="e21">严厉<Denoter did="d21" type="action">追究</Denoter><Participant oid="o21">事故责任者</Participant></Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph>
　　<Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e22"><Time tid="t22" type="relTime">目前</Time>，<Participant oid="o22,o23">伤者</Participant>已被<Denoter did="d22" type="movement">送往</Denoter><Location lid="l22">雅江县医院</Location></Event><Event eid="e23"><Denoter did="d23" type="operation">救治</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e24"><Participant sid="s24,s25,s26">甘孜州代理州长益西达瓦任</Participant>已率领工作组<Denoter did="d24" type="movement">赶到</Denoter><Location lid="l24">现场</Location></Event><Event eid="e25">开展<Denoter did="d25" type="action">善后</Denoter></Event>、/w <Event eid="e26"><Object oid="o26">事故</Object><Denoter did="d26" type="operation">调查</Denoter></Event>等工作，<Event eid="e27"><Object oid="o27,o28">事故原因</Object><Participant sid="s27,s28">调查组</Participant>正在进一步<Denoter did="d27" type="operation">调查</Denoter></Event><Event eid="e28"><Denoter did="d28" type="operation">核实</Denoter></Event>中。</Sentence></Paragraph></Content>
